{"questionId":"13816009","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The cost of a journey on the different boat routes is given in the following table; all prices are given in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>USD</mi></math>. The cost of a journey is the same in either direction between two ports.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/f8c5fd340751d010c11ffcea6632ac8f6a9ba4a5.png\"></p>\n<p>Sofia wants to make a trip where she travels on each of the boat routes at least once, beginning and ending at port <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the minimum cost of Sofia’s trip.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>cost of their Eulerian trail <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math> <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>180</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>consider edges to get from <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(</strong><strong>M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>235</mn><mo> </mo><mfenced><mi>USD</mi></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"13816009","referenceCode":"23N.2.AHL.TZ0.5d","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the minimum cost of